summary: I'll never get over the moment when Spider-Man Noir is guessing which colors were which on the rubiks cube and my colorblind...
body: I’ll never get over the moment when Spider-Man Noir is guessing which colors were which on the rubiks cube and my colorblind brother turning to me to say “hey, that’s familiar” and the entire theater being subjected to my asthmatic wheeze followed by the most unladylike snort of laughter.

reblog.comment: I’ll never get over the moment when Spider-Man Noir is guessing which colors were which on the rubiks cube and my colorblind brother turning to me to say “hey, that’s familiar” and the entire theater being subjected to my asthmatic wheeze followed by the most unladylike snort of laughter.

summary: Patreon reward for @narrev of a pinup of Doc Ock from Into The Spider Verse as a gift for @mydetheturk! I am SO frikkin in love...
caption:
Patreon reward for @narrev of a pinup of Doc Ock from Into The Spider Verse as a gift for @mydetheturk!

I am SO frikkin in love with this iteration of Doc Ock and have been pretty much infatuated with every aspect of her character since the moment she was on screen, so this was a real treat for me to work on and I’m so pleased with how she turned out!
